# Top-level backend dependencies.
#
# This file is the source of truth for direct dependencies. The full
# transitive dependency tree (with hashes for supply-chain security) is
# compiled to requirements.lock via:
#
#     uv pip compile backend/requirements.in \
#         -o backend/requirements.lock --generate-hashes
#
# Workflow for adding/updating a backend dependency:
#   1. Edit this file.
#   2. Re-run the uv pip compile command above.
#   3. Commit both requirements.in and requirements.lock together.
#
# Dependabot monitors requirements.in (see .github/dependabot.yml). When
# it opens a PR bumping a version here, regenerate the lock file and
# amend it into the same PR.

